{"tid":885711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又係個別案件】林鄭三度被日傳媒問：香港自由是否倒退？","createTime":"2018-11-01T13:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T15:25:07.000Z","uid":78546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c19d17c5f350d4357a2b23b152b8c874bc4520","tid":885711,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181101&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58862178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181101%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58862178&d=rhwCuyOkgID7OebO1yMOFsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=20000412\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181101%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58862178&h=1b756034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181101&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58862178</a><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥連日出席貿發局在日本東京舉行的「Think Global, think HK」活動，在訪問環節中，日本傳媒四次發問，三度質疑香港自由社會包括新聞自由是否倒退，不少更是針對《金融時報》編輯馬凱簽證不獲續發有關，更有日本記者問香港回歸21年後，會否變了中國另一個城市。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回答時指出，香港回歸中國已21年，一直奉行一國兩制，並形容這個制度是香港利益所在，香港亦奉行法治、自由等。她說：「喺你問題入面有講過香港自由是否倒退的顧慮，但呢樣要證據去證明，香港有過百個駐地記者，報道香港、中國、亞洲，已經係自由嘅證明。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到馬凱為甚麼不能續簽證，林鄭月娥指出，各國都有入境政策，個別案件不能續一評論，而該名人士亦已上訴，只能說香港政府是根據法律執行入境政策。<br />\n<br />\n回答最後一條關於香港自由倒退的問題時，林鄭指部份人對香港的主觀印象難以控制，但香港在全球調查上亦有良好排行，「你嚟香港做嘢感受下，並非好似其他報道或你聽到咁。」<br />\n<br />\n她又說除了是次記者發問外，是次外訪從未有其他在日本會面的人問過相關問題，「不過我歡迎發問。」"},{"pid":"08d7f66f97046a6f191e5a9356b39fe83794cf4e","tid":885711,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fad1b7b0a03e0c7a07046c3e8e77184ab01757c9","tid":885711,"uid":137725,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"08d7f66f97046a6f191e5a9356b39fe83794cf4e","tid":885711,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"u = on9<br />\n<br />\nexplain = no need"},{"pid":"ffe9ace3d711c8e7c8b458e233a6d0ff8a4ed3a3","tid":885711,"uid":149844,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"連日本仔都知一國兩制係講大話<br />\n笑你班港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778901caf4e53346fdc7f2bd2958a976e62b56ee","tid":885711,"uid":41818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"反而日本記者敢問 香港嗰班？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49bc1294a75adbc53cdce4dfcdb46453e79a689","tid":885711,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"中國特色香港法律"},{"pid":"ce3c42cad0c4a201dc487f44d4a29149ff08fde3","tid":885711,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffe9ace3d711c8e7c8b458e233a6d0ff8a4ed3a3","tid":885711,"uid":149844,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"連日本仔都知一國兩制係講大話<br />\n笑你班港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"日本好留意港台中"},{"pid":"c9c7cfb0d4753c806cc80024295d09ec16f51ecc","tid":885711,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4f8d8a11298acf9cc837325a2ca5505cf5ae95","tid":885711,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29fcd5c60957ba1675defd433aa21e8101ca0c01","tid":885711,"uid":188396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"778901caf4e53346fdc7f2bd2958a976e62b56ee","tid":885711,"uid":41818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"反而日本記者敢問 香港嗰班？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"香港記者不嬲垃圾嚟<img src=\"/assets